
UC28 View Patients

The iTrust user (LCHP) has been authenticated in the iTrust Medical Records system [[requirements:uc3(UC3)]].

The LHCP chooses to view all patients with which he or she has ever had an office visit with. The patientâ€™s name (clickable to view PHR), address, and date of last office visit are displayed. The list is sorted by the date of the last office visit (most recent first).

